OL,6,FSickness absence in the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Civil Service (NICS) has grown
OL,8,Fto an average of more than 13 days
OL,9,Flost per staff member in a year, a
OL,10,Freport has found.
OL,12,FAuditor General Dorinnia Carville said
OL,13,Fthe annual cost of sickness levels was
OL,14,Fnow close to #50 million.
OL,16,FShe also found that last year there
OL,17,Fwere close to 5,500 vacant posts in
OL,18,Fthe Civil Service.
