OL,6,FThe auditor said NICS has "not
OL,7,Fdelivered the scale and pace of reform
OL,8,Fnecessary to demonstrate value for
OL,9,Fmoney in its workforce and people
OL,10,Fmanagement".
OL,12,FIn April 2025, the Civil Service
OL,13,Fworkforce in Northern Ireland was
OL,14,F24,500. Its pay bill last year was
OL,15,F#1.27 billion.
OL,17,FIt is the third-largest public sector
OL,18,Femployer in the region, after health
OL,19,Fand education.
