OL,6,FThe Audit Office has published a
OL,7,Ffollow-up to its 2020 report into
OL,8,FNICS, stating that many problems it
OL,9,Fpreviously highlighted have escalated.
OL,11,FThe report found:
OL,13,F` There were nearly 5,500 vacant posts
OL,14,Fdeclared by the NICS on March 31 2025.
OL,16,F` There is a "greater reliance on
OL,17,Ftemporary staffing solutions". The
OL,18,Freport said nearly 5,000 agency
OL,19,Fworkers were employed last April, more
OL,20,Fthan double the number recorded in
OL,21,FApril 2019.
