OL,6,F` More than 3,000 NICS staff were
OL,7,Ftemporarily promoted (representing 13%
OL,8,Fof the workforce).
OL,10,F` Sickness absence levels have risen
OL,11,Fto an average of 13.4 days lost per
OL,12,Fstaff year in 2024-25, compared with
OL,13,F12.6 days in 2018-19.
OL,15,F` 57.6% of staff recorded no sickness
OL,16,Fdays in year.
OL,18,F` The costs associated with sickness
OL,19,Fabsence have also increased, from
OL,20,F#32.9 million in 2018-19 to #48.8
OL,21,Fmillion in 2024-25.
