OL,6,FThe report said there has been a "lack
OL,7,Fof progress in key strategic areas,
OL,8,Fsuch as workforce planning and
OL,9,Frecruitment".
OL,11,FIt also expressed concern over the
OL,12,Faffordability of filling vacant posts.
OL,14,FMs Carville said a number of
OL,15,Frecommendations from the 2020 Audit
OL,16,FOffice report are still to be
OL,17,Fimplemented.
