OL,6,FHer latest report said there had been
OL,7,Fimprovements in enhanced governance
OL,8,Farrangements with the establishment of
OL,9,Fa People Committee, a new People
OL,10,FStrategy for 2025-30, and the launch
OL,11,Fof new apprenticeship, student and
OL,12,Fwork placement programmes.
OL,14,FHowever, it said that "without
OL,15,Fsustained, collective leadership and
OL,16,Furgent delivery, the NICS is at
OL,17,Fcontinued risk of failing to
OL,18,Fdemonstrate value for money".
