OL,6,FMs Carville said: "Strong leadership
OL,7,Fand a right-sized workforce that has
OL,8,Fthe requisite skills are essential for
OL,9,Fthe NICS to successfully deliver
OL,10,Fcritical public services and meet the
OL,11,Fpriorities set out in the 2024`2027
OL,12,FProgramme for Government.
OL,14,F"This requires a modernised approach
OL,15,Fto how the workforce is planned,
OL,16,Frecruited and managed.
